75g spready butter
80g golden syrup
1/3 flat tsp salt
140g oats
10g chia in ~30ml water
15g linseeds
50g pumpkin seeds
45g sunflower seeds
35g cranberries


Mix together the dry ingredients except the salt.
Soak the chia seeds in the water
Line a tin with paper
Melt butter and sugars in pan and add salt
Oven on at 175C
Unclump the chia seeds and mix into the pan
Add all the dry ingredients, mix well and press into pan
25 min in oven

